# Runtime Session Data

This directory contains temporary state for sub-agent orchestration sessions.

**Structure**:
```
.sia/runtime/
└── {session_id}/           # UUID v4 per orchestration session
    ├── orchestrator.yaml   # SUPER_AGENT orchestration state
    ├── agent-1/
    │   ├── status.yaml     # Progress tracking (polled every 2s)
    │   ├── output.md       # SPR final output
    │   ├── progress.log    # Timestamped events
    │   └── logs/           # Copilot CLI logs (--log-dir)
    └── agent-2/
        └── ...
```

**Lifecycle**:
- Created: On `orchestrate_subagents.spawn_parallel()`
- Updated: Sub-agents auto-update `status.yaml` every 30s
- Cleaned: Auto-purge sessions older than 7 days

**DO NOT** commit session data to git (transient state only).
